Differential Impact of COVID-19 on Norovirus and Campylobacter in England: Detailed results

Nikola Ondrikova

Custom tsglm function

NbinomTsglm <- function(outcome_ts, predictors){
  ### function with our model definition
  
  set.seed(123589)
  model_fit <- tsglm(ts = outcome_ts,
                     xreg = predictors,
                     model = list(past_obs=c(1)),
                     distr = "nbinom", link = 'log') 
  return(model_fit)
}
